headline: Chinese Robotics Company Geekplus Eyes New Listing as It Nears Profitability
summary: Geekplus, a known name in warehouse robotics with customers like Walmart, Adidas and UPS, is betting it can dominate the market as more companies use robots for industrial tasks.
